    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 78-81.</p><p>Legendary AC</p><p>At 20th level, if your AC calculation is lower than your level, you can use your level as your AC instead. If you are using your Legendary AC, you cannot further increase your AC in any way, except by temporary AC increases or magical effects lasting 1 hour or less. Other spells and effects that increase your AC only affect your regular AC.</p><p>Cantrips</p><p>Prepared</p><p>— Spell Slots Per Spell Level — 1st 2nd 3rd 4th 5th 6th 7th 8th 9th 10th</p><p>Known</p><p>Spells</p></div>",
